---> Write down why each of the entries in the left column will raise a syntax error if it is used as an identifier

1) The identifier contains space which is not allowed in Python
2) The identifier contains - (Python variables can only contain letters(lowercase or uppercase) & numbers (0 to 9) or underscore character(_))
3) The identifier is a keyword
4) The identifier starts with a number

